Project Description
This is Part 1 of the Chat Application POE. It implements a registration and login system with validation rules.

Features Implemented

1. Username Validation (`checkUserName()`)
- Must contain an underscore (`_`)
- Maximum length of 5 characters
- Returns `true` if valid, `false` otherwise

2. Password Validation (`checkPasswordComplexity()`)
- Minimum 8 characters long
- Contains at least 1 capital letter
- Contains at least 1 number
- Contains at least 1 special character
- Returns `true` if valid, `false` otherwise

3. Phone Number Validation (`checkCellPhoneNumber()`)
- Must start with South African international code `+27`
- Appropriate length for SA numbers
- Returns `true` if valid, `false` otherwise

